Source.Name: mono-msbuild
Source.Summary: the build platform for .NET and Visual Studio
Source.Description: The Microsoft Build Engine is a platform for building applications. This engine, which is also known as MSBuild, provides an XML schema for a project file that controls how the build platform processes and builds software.
